body:
Red panda

I use to call you my red panda.

But if you’re Retsuko then I’m your space cadet.

Trying my best for you but being to oblivious to see past the edge of my nose.

The truth is, I’m not empty minded, I just get lost in your eyes.

The truth is, it’s not that I cant talk, you just leave me speechless.

The truth is, love turns me into a space cadet and you’re a universe I could spend my lifetime exploring.

So, Retsuko, red panda, I’ll forever be lost in you

summary: Hey so I have struggled for a very long time to get more comfortable with digital painting, especially in Photoshop. So today I...
caption:
Hey so I have struggled for a very long time to get more comfortable with digital painting, especially in Photoshop. So today I sat down and watched some speedpaints to get inspired and begun painting something. 

I decided to draw one of my favourite scenes of Haida from the Aggretsuko show. This is one of my favourite versions of Haida. Sulky, drunk, with red cheeks and his cool casual outfit. Makes me weak…

It’s been a while since I felt this good while painting. I let myself take the time I needed and the result isn’t too bad either!
